    "4096", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "f4c74bc0-53cb-4833-9d7e-d4b9bd8c0fc4"], Cell[TextData[{
     "the number of shots (",
     Cell[BoxData[
     "default_shots"], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
