Cell["\<\
With an active IBM Quantum Platform connection, submit a circuit and get back \
a job handle (the call returns immediately, while the job sits in the queue):\
\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"7880a39f-4f35-4c33-a2c1-7a34921108e5"],

Cell["\<\
job = IBMJobSubmit[QuantumCircuitOperator[{\"GHZ\", \"Fourier\"[3], {1, 2, \
3}}], \"ibm_fez\"]\
\>", "Program",ExpressionUUID->"7d2f7894-beaf-479b-a604-02e14ff41344"],

Cell["\t", "ExampleDelimiter",ExpressionUUID->"c4f88249-8532-40b8-8c69-f41f3f54d9f5"],

Cell["\<\
Once the job completes, the handle's default output is the measurement \
reconstructed from the hardware counts, in the Wolfram Language qubit order:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"b666ae45-f86e-40d2-ab41-61a44ce75f80"],

Cell["job[\"Refresh\"][]", "Program",ExpressionUUID->"c80e9dab-5f62-40a7-924f-f1d5eb16e2a4"],

